{"tid":831281,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人食月餅嗰陣係咁","createTime":"2018-09-21T19:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T08:29:47.000Z","uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e00a3e4bb4555e9c27d49bad3e7d85bf47ddd04f","tid":831281,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"拆開個包裝袋,切8份<br />\n食最多蛋黃嗰兩份,其餘留返俾屋企人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果到下次食嗰陣,其餘6份未清曬<br />\n唔撚理,照拆個新既黎食最多黃嗰兩份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後俾老母話衰格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明知屋企多人鍾意食蛋黃年啦<br />\n親戚同老母係都要咁固執<br />\n年年買雙黃蓮蓉俾我地<br />\n買三黃/四黃咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7695d8a5971bf6d78e9e90a45c5b9802098cf1f","tid":831281,"uid":183601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T19:55:47.000Z","msg":"傳統月餅一次起碼食半舊啦, 妹下妹下咁"},{"pid":"19b77c25372ed60c7503d99265f93c95ef421594","tid":831281,"uid":199938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T21:24:50.000Z","msg":"切四份都嫌細 <br />\n<br />\n總之一定攞成個黃嗰個"},{"pid":"e72e90bb3a69e070b12a942e821e18bd0bce0732","tid":831281,"uid":139156,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T21:58:21.000Z","msg":"樓主賤格"},{"pid":"1faa886e3cfc08287c023596437e446843a5eabc","tid":831281,"uid":83446,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T22:12:14.000Z","msg":"成舊就咁啪架喎<br />\n仲切黎切去咁麻煩?"},{"pid":"e61c8d9cd5e607ae4017af44b654faa3084cd516","tid":831281,"uid":8786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:44:12.000Z","msg":"切乜撚一隻叉吉落去挖個黃出黎食d蓮蓉同個皮要食架咩？"},{"pid":"a873b5203cf2971c78d8c6d67e4ad410f26502cd","tid":831281,"uid":8883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"自己落街買隻鹹蛋啪啦on9"},{"pid":"d1017ad3cb0be6f0adabd6933fd91b3c444eb097","tid":831281,"uid":33359